---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Container class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-16 md:space-y-20">
      <section class="grid gap-10 md:gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary">
            What is EzWin Academy?
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            An online math tuition for Primary School, but a lil better
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            EzWin Academy is a next-generation online math tuition centre
            dedicated to primary school students in Singapore. We combine
            personalised instruction, smart digital resources, and a supportive
            community to help every child build deep understanding,
            problem-solving confidence, and long-term mastery. With a focus on
            parent partnership and transparent progress updates, EzWin Academy
            believes every child deserves a learning journey tailored to their
            strengths and needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary">
            Founder story
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            From coding educator to math mentor
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Haris Samingan has 7 years of teaching experience and a background
            as an Ex-Google Developer Expert. He has taught at NTU, SMU, ACS(I),
            MGS, and Singapore Sports School. In 2025, he brought that expertise
            to mathematics, creating EzWin Academy to blend rigorous teaching
            with technology so every student can feel supported and capable.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-primary">
            How is EzWin Academy different?
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900">
            Personalised, transparent, and parent-first
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-gray-700">
            <li>
              • Smart practice plans that prioritise the highest-impact topics
              for each student.
            </li>
            <li>
              • A single guiding value: be the parent you wish you
              had—supportive, honest, and focused on growth.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
